OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,FAn asylum seeker who was inside a
OL,7,Fhotel when it was attacked by a mob of
OL,8,Frioters has told ITV News that he
OL,9,Fthought he was going to be "burned
OL,10,Falive."
OL,12,FAli - not his real name - was in the
OL,13,FHoliday Inn Express in Wath-upon-
OL,14,FDearne, near Rotherham, when hundreds
OL,15,Fof protesters who gathered outside
OL,16,Fthrew missiles and tried to set fire
OL,17,Fto the building on 4 August.
OL,19,FAli said he is still "traumatised" by
OL,20,Fthe events of that day.
