OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,F"When I saw smoke, we were all inside
OL,7,Fand we thought we will be burned alive
OL,8,F- sometimes when I am asleep I see
OL,9,Fthis again," he said.
OL,11,F"We heard them smash windows with
OL,12,Fbricks. They threw missiles - we heard
OL,13,Fsuch a noise.JIf it wasn't for the
OL,14,Fpolice we would have died."
OL,16,FAli said the hotel staff had warned
OL,17,Fthe asylum seekers ahead of the riot
OL,18,Fnot to go out but that he had not
OL,19,Fexpected such violence.
