OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,FAli said he thought he was going to
OL,7,Fdie.
OL,9,FHe said: "I thought I would never see
OL,10,Fmy family again. We smelled the smoke
OL,11,Fand we didn't want to be inside but
OL,12,Fthey smashed windows... It was many
OL,13,Fpeople, so we daren't go outside."
OL,15,F"Thank you to the police because we
OL,16,Fwould be dead if they hadn't helped us.
OL,18,F"I saw with my own eyes a policeman
OL,19,Flying on the floor hurt. And a female
OL,20,Fpolice (officer). God bless them."
