OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,FAli, who has been moved to a different
OL,7,Flocation since the disorder, said that
OL,8,Fhe would not feel safe to return to
OL,9,FRotherham.
OL,11,F"I would like people like this to
OL,12,Flearn about us - we are not so
OL,13,Fdifferent. I know some people, asylum
OL,14,Fseekers, do bad things but not most
OL,15,Fpeople."
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Police said 118 people
OL,18,Fhave been arrested over the disorder
OL,19,Fso far while 33 people have been
OL,20,Fsentenced.
