OL,3,C'I feared l'd be burned alive': Asylum
OL,4,Cseeker in hotel attacked by mob
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, 4 September, a 13-year-
OL,7,Fold boy became the youngest person to
OL,8,Fbe convicted over the trouble outside
OL,9,Fthe South Yorkshire hotel.
OL,11,FThe court heard that the teenager had
OL,12,Fthrown a lit firework and stones at
OL,13,Fpolice guarding the hotel.
